#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:2
#: 222e70feb116465faeb88d4397d76a74
msgid "Differentiability"
msgstr "可微性"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:4
#: f1d6ecd0b31d4e8a9acddc661eaf5cb1
msgid ""
"Every component along the ``Mesh → Assembler → SparseMatrix → Condenser → "
"Solve`` pipeline is either a :class:`torch.nn.Module` or a custom "
":class:`torch.autograd.Function`, and the linear solve at the end has an "
"**analytic adjoint backward**. As a result a loss computed on the FEM "
"solution can be back-propagated all the way to *anything* that touched the "
"pipeline: a coefficient at every node, a Dirichlet value, or a neural "
"network that parameterises the material coefficient field --- without "
"writing a single line of sensitivity code by hand."
msgstr ""
"``Mesh → Assembler → SparseMatrix → Condenser → Solve`` 流水线上的每一个组件，要么是 "
":class:`torch.nn.Module`\\ ，要么是自定义的 :class:`torch.autograd.Function`\\ "
"，而末端的线性求解具备\\ **解析的伴随反向传播**\\ 。其结果是：在有限元解上计算出的损失，可以一路反向传播到\\ *任何*\\ "
"接触过流水线的对象：每个节点上的系数、某个狄利克雷取值，或是参数化材料系数场的神经网络——而无需手写一行灵敏度代码。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:15
#: 7c4d4ff7a2ea4b78a85555a325035fd0
msgid ""
"This chapter explains how the gradient flow works, demonstrates it with two "
"worked examples (parameter identification and density-based topology "
"optimization), and lists the cost, correctness, and the few things that "
"aren't differentiable yet."
msgstr "本章讲解梯度流是如何工作的，用两个实战示例（参数辨识与基于密度的拓扑优化）加以演示，并列出其开销、正确性，以及目前尚不可微的少数情形。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:22
#: 242ca60d5ba14193b7523922d2c628ed
msgid "How it works"
msgstr "工作原理"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:24
#: deb70ffbe8e1474ba50c03073a3a3e29
msgid "Three pieces of TensorMesh are wired into the autograd graph:"
msgstr "TensorMesh 有三个部件接入了 autograd 计算图："

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:26
#: cf27e55d98c8497bb93f8ff475be180b
msgid ""
":class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` extends :class:`torch.nn.Module`. Its ``points`` "
"and per-node fields are tensors that can carry ``requires_grad=True``. "
"Moving the mesh with ``mesh.to(device)`` and saving with ``state_dict`` work"
" as you'd expect."
msgstr ""
":class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` 继承自 :class:`torch.nn.Module`\\ 。它的 ``points`` "
"与逐节点字段都是可以携带 ``requires_grad=True`` 的张量。用 ``mesh.to(device)`` 搬移网格、用 "
"``state_dict`` 保存网格，都会如你所料地工作。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:30
#: 506ea217e61b4aae8ddbb632886d214e
msgid ""
":class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler` and :class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler`"
" are themselves ``nn.Module`` s. Any tensor that flows into a "
"``forward(...)`` integrand becomes a graph input to the assembled matrix or "
"vector."
msgstr ""
":class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler` 和 :class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler` "
"本身就是 ``nn.Module``\\ 。任何流入 ``forward(...)`` 被积函数的张量，都会成为装配出的矩阵或向量的计算图输入。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:34
#: 11b77f09fc3b4524ad7080351779889d
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
":meth:`tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix.solve` is inherited unchanged from "
"``torch_sla.SparseTensor`` (see :doc:`linear_solvers`), so the adjoint lives"
" in ``torch-sla`` rather than in TensorMesh. The forward solve produces "
":math:`u` from :math:`A\\,u = b`. For a scalar loss :math:`L(u)`, reverse-"
"mode autograd hands the solve the upstream gradient :math:`\\partial "
"L/\\partial u`; rather than differentiate through the solver's internals, "
"the solve is wrapped in a :class:`torch.autograd.Function` whose custom "
"``backward`` solves a single **adjoint** system for the adjoint variable "
":math:`\\boldsymbol{\\lambda}`,"
msgstr ""
":meth:`tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix.solve` 原封不动地继承自 "
"``torch_sla.SparseTensor``\\ （见 :doc:`linear_solvers`\\ ），因此伴随逻辑位于 ``torch-"
"sla`` 中而非 TensorMesh 内。前向求解由 :math:`A\\,u = b` 得到 :math:`u`\\ 。对于标量损失 "
":math:`L(u)`\\ ，反向模式 autograd 会将上游梯度 :math:`\\partial L/\\partial u` "
"交给该求解；它并不穿过求解器的内部进行求导，而是把求解封装进一个 :class:`torch.autograd.Function`\\ ，其自定义的 "
"``backward`` 求解单个\\ **伴随**\\ 系统以得到伴随变量 :math:`\\boldsymbol{\\lambda}`\\ ，"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:45
#: ba93b3ee5ac248d7b74bf8f43d640661
#, python-brace-format
msgid "A^{T}\\, \\boldsymbol{\\lambda} \\;=\\; \\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial u},"
msgstr "A^{T}\\, \\boldsymbol{\\lambda} \\;=\\; \\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial u},"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:49
#: 559f9f0887d3483381714de0f4c697b6
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"and then assembles the input gradients in closed form — for each non-zero "
"matrix entry :math:`\\partial L / \\partial A_{ij} = -\\lambda_i\\, u_j`, "
"and for the right-hand side :math:`\\partial L / \\partial b = "
"\\boldsymbol{\\lambda}`."
msgstr ""
"随后以闭式形式装配出输入梯度——对每个非零矩阵元 :math:`\\partial L / \\partial A_{ij} = "
"-\\lambda_i\\, u_j`\\ ，对右端项 :math:`\\partial L / \\partial b = "
"\\boldsymbol{\\lambda}`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:54
#: ca57b41b498b443b82b99f3d5c61ebc4
msgid ""
"A call to ``loss = criterion(K.solve(b), target).sum()`` followed by "
"``loss.backward()`` therefore gives correct gradients for every leaf tensor "
"that fed into ``K``, ``b``, or the loss --- matrix entries, source terms, "
"prescribed boundary values, and any upstream parameter (NN weights, design "
"variables, …)."
msgstr ""
"因此，先调用 ``loss = criterion(K.solve(b), target).sum()`` 再调用 "
"``loss.backward()``\\ ，便能为所有流入 ``K``\\ 、\\ ``b`` "
"或损失的叶子张量给出正确梯度——矩阵元、源项、给定的边界取值，以及任何上游参数（神经网络权重、设计变量等）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:62
#: 149499a71cdd4eeb9b73b3fa765bd75c
msgid "Adjoint cost"
msgstr "伴随方法的开销"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:64
#: 4af3a4c5f60940198058c36d3542ed00
msgid ""
"Back-propagation through one linear solve costs **one additional sparse "
"solve** (with the transposed system). For SPD problems :math:`A^T = A`, so "
"the backward uses the same factorisation or preconditioner pattern as the "
"forward. The total per-iteration cost in a gradient-based optimiser is "
"therefore roughly ``2 × forward_solve_cost`` regardless of how many degrees "
"of freedom you have or how complex the assembly logic is."
msgstr ""
"穿过一次线性求解的反向传播，只需付出\\ **一次额外的稀疏求解**\\ （针对转置系统）。对于 SPD 问题 :math:`A^T = A`\\ "
"，因此反向传播使用与前向相同的分解或预条件子模式。由此，在基于梯度的优化器中，每次迭代的总开销大约为 ``2 × "
"forward_solve_cost``\\ ，与你有多少自由度、装配逻辑多么复杂无关。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:74
#: 607795f905684ad58cdfb2f97f7385c3
msgid "Correctness check: autograd vs finite differences"
msgstr "正确性校验：autograd 对比有限差分"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:76
#: c781f088936b4be0b340e7f78c1c3d76
msgid ""
"Before trusting autograd on a serious inverse problem, it is worth spot-"
"checking it against central finite differences. The script that produces the"
" figures on this page contains a small check on a 35-node mesh; running it "
"prints"
msgstr ""
"在把 autograd 用于正经的反问题之前，值得拿中心有限差分对它做一次抽查。生成本页各图的脚本中包含了一个在 35 "
"节点网格上的小型校验；运行它会打印出"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:89
#: de0823e01762482ebd76b815f287db88
msgid ""
"i.e. roughly 11 digits of agreement, which is what a float64 adjoint should "
"give. The minor residual is the FD truncation error, not an autograd bug."
msgstr ""
"即大约 11 位有效数字的吻合，这正是 float64 伴随方法应当达到的水平。那点微小的残差是有限差分的截断误差，而非 autograd 的缺陷。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:95
#: 93b1f2572ee14767a263760ad0dace71
msgid "What's differentiable, what isn't"
msgstr "什么可微，什么不可微"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:97
#: f35e51244ad34a8494cb1915d03849a9
msgid "**Differentiable through ``solve`` today:**"
msgstr "**目前可穿过 ``solve`` 求导的对象：**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:99
#: 60f86b3d7568456ebde8d237ad8236c9
msgid ""
"Matrix entries (``edata``) -- gradients land on the upstream tensor whose "
"values fed each non-zero."
msgstr "矩阵元（\\ ``edata``\\ ）——梯度会落到提供各非零值的那个上游张量上。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:101
#: 4fa15520cf6744ccbc39996ac29897e9
msgid "The right-hand side ``b``."
msgstr "右端项 ``b``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:102
#: 4a317356577c40139b7f01020f203da9
msgid ""
"Any tensor in ``point_data`` / ``element_data`` / ``scalar_data`` passed to "
"an assembler -- gradients flow through the integrand."
msgstr ""
"传给装配器的 ``point_data`` / ``element_data`` / ``scalar_data`` "
"中的任何张量——梯度会穿过被积函数流动。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:104
#: f52bbe3c9a8444419f3faf4a30d9fd4d
msgid "Dirichlet values (via the condensed RHS contribution)."
msgstr "狄利克雷取值（通过凝聚后对右端项的贡献）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:106
#: 594e709781bb4944920ddea5564de472
msgid "**Backend caveats:**"
msgstr "**后端方面的注意事项：**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:108
#: d882a64f6751465d86fbab0360fe52ea
msgid ""
"The ``torch-sla`` ``backend=\"pytorch\"`` and ``backend=\"auto\"`` paths are"
" the safest defaults for autograd. They route the forward through a pure-"
"PyTorch iterative solver and use the analytic adjoint for backward."
msgstr ""
"``torch-sla`` 的 ``backend=\"pytorch\"`` 和 ``backend=\"auto\"`` 路径是对 autograd"
" 最稳妥的默认选择。它们将前向路由到纯 PyTorch 的迭代求解器，反向则使用解析伴随。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:112
#: e075a4c1ce9540b6a7fb370e9292e0e8
msgid ""
"The SciPy / Eigen / cuDSS / CuPy backends are wrapped by the same custom "
":class:`torch.autograd.Function`, so gradients still flow -- but the forward"
" computation lives in NumPy / CuPy / C++ and detaches from the graph for "
"that span. This is correct for the linear solve but means you cannot \"see "
"into\" the solver from autograd."
msgstr ""
"SciPy / Eigen / cuDSS / CuPy 后端都被同一个自定义 :class:`torch.autograd.Function` "
"包装，因此梯度依然能够流动——但前向计算发生在 NumPy / CuPy / C++ "
"中，并在那一段从计算图上脱离。这对线性求解而言是正确的，但意味着你无法从 autograd “看进”求解器内部。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:118
#: 9f3808b15bc44a8b84d8c33faf3745a0
msgid ""
"The legacy fallback paths in :mod:`tensormesh.sparse` (used when ``torch-"
"sla`` is not installed) implement the same custom ``autograd.Function`` with"
" adjoint backward, so gradients work there too."
msgstr ""
":mod:`tensormesh.sparse` 中的遗留回退路径（在未安装 ``torch-sla`` 时使用）实现了同样的、带伴随反向传播的自定义 "
"``autograd.Function``\\ ，所以在那里梯度同样有效。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:123
#: b20d43f047084dcf984dda4a757c3257
msgid ""
"When in doubt for a research workflow involving autodiff, install ``torch-"
"sla`` and stick with ``backend=\"auto\"``."
msgstr "在涉及自动微分的研究工作流中拿不准时，请安装 ``torch-sla`` 并坚持使用 ``backend=\"auto\"``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:128
#: 27f21ea1ac3648248555b5d834f001e4
msgid "Worked example 1: coefficient-field identification"
msgstr "实战示例 1：系数场辨识"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:130
#: df58e10300e74f138e73b4fa32e31216
msgid ""
"Suppose we observe a \"ground truth\" Poisson solution and want to recover "
"the unknown coefficient field :math:`\\kappa(x)` at every mesh node by "
"gradient descent:"
msgstr "假设我们观测到一个“真值”泊松解，并希望通过梯度下降，在每个网格节点上恢复未知的系数场 :math:`\\kappa(x)`\\ ："

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:134
#: 58f08a1d13924a45a4d6542c1b941da4
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"-\\nabla \\cdot \\big(\\kappa(x)\\, \\nabla u\\big) \\;=\\; f \\quad \\text{in } \\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad u = 0 \\text{ on } \\partial\\Omega."
msgstr ""
"-\\nabla \\cdot \\big(\\kappa(x)\\, \\nabla u\\big) \\;=\\; f \\quad \\text{in } \\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad u = 0 \\text{ on } \\partial\\Omega."

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:139
#: db96e8538fa94c1d9e0d926a82140ece
msgid ""
"The forward map is \"FEM-solve given :math:`\\kappa`\"; the loss is the L² "
"distance between the FEM solution and the observation; autograd supplies the"
" gradient and Adam updates :math:`\\kappa`. We parametrise :math:`\\kappa = "
"1 + \\tanh\\theta` so :math:`\\kappa` stays in :math:`(0, 2)` -- strictly "
"positive, hence the FEM matrix is SPD on every iteration -- with "
":math:`\\theta` unconstrained."
msgstr ""
"前向映射是“给定 :math:`\\kappa` 后做有限元求解”；损失是有限元解与观测之间的 L² 距离；autograd 提供梯度，Adam 更新 "
":math:`\\kappa`\\ 。我们将其参数化为 :math:`\\kappa = 1 + \\tanh\\theta`\\ ，从而让 "
":math:`\\kappa` 保持在 :math:`(0, 2)` 内——严格为正，因此有限元矩阵在每次迭代都是 SPD——而 "
":math:`\\theta` 无约束。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:189
#: 8667c5aa7f4e466e819d8340cdb4bd8a
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Over 5000 iterations the data loss drops by more than seven orders of "
"magnitude and the max-norm observation error bottoms out near :math:`6 "
"\\times 10^{-5}`:"
msgstr "在 5000 次迭代中，数据损失下降了七个数量级以上，最大范数下的观测误差最终降至约 :math:`6 \\times 10^{-5}`\\ ："

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:197
#: 619158b8f5704b51a757096109aea1e4
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Adam optimisation history over 5000 steps: the data loss :math:`\\|u_\\theta"
" - u_{\\rm obs}\\|_2^2` falls from :math:`10^{-2}` to :math:`\\sim 3 \\times"
" 10^{-10}` (the periodic spikes are Adam overshooting, recovered within a "
"few steps), and the relative max-norm error in :math:`u` reaches "
":math:`\\sim 6 \\times 10^{-5}`."
msgstr ""
"5000 步的 Adam 优化历程：数据损失 :math:`\\|u_\\theta - u_{\\rm obs}\\|_2^2` 从 "
":math:`10^{-2}` 降至 :math:`\\sim 3 \\times 10^{-10}`\\ （周期性的尖峰是 Adam "
"的过冲，几步之内即可恢复），\\ :math:`u` 的相对最大范数误差达到 :math:`\\sim 6 \\times 10^{-5}`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:203
#: 76b57b7dc5f74aa880c9f6fb1f749445
msgid "The recovered coefficient field:"
msgstr "恢复出的系数场："

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:209
#: 47ca02ecc6c846a4b8e532a282b03035
msgid ""
"Ground truth :math:`\\kappa(x)` (left), the field recovered after 5000 Adam "
"steps (middle), and the absolute error (right). The four-lobe checkerboard "
"is now recovered across the whole domain; only a faint residual remains at "
"the centre (absolute error peaking near :math:`0.08` there, under "
":math:`0.01` over the rest of the domain), where the solution gradient is "
"small."
msgstr ""
"真值 :math:`\\kappa(x)`\\ （左），经 5000 步 Adam "
"后恢复的场（中），以及绝对误差（右）。如今四瓣棋盘格已在整个求解域上恢复出来；仅在中心残留一抹微弱的痕迹（那里绝对误差峰值约为 "
":math:`0.08`\\ ，而在求解域其余部分低于 :math:`0.01`\\ ），该处的解梯度很小。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:216
#: 6d2b1bb4103a4007a001f1286a88a9bd
msgid ""
"The only visible residual is a faint blob at the centre. There the constant "
"source makes :math:`\\nabla u` vanish, so the flux :math:`\\kappa\\,\\nabla "
"u` carries almost no information about :math:`\\kappa` and that region is "
"recovered slowest -- a smoothness penalty on :math:`\\theta` removes it, "
"left as an exercise."
msgstr ""
"唯一可见的残差是中心处一团微弱的色斑。在那里常数源使 :math:`\\nabla u` 消失，因此通量 "
":math:`\\kappa\\,\\nabla u` 几乎不携带任何关于 :math:`\\kappa` 的信息，该区域恢复得最慢——对 "
":math:`\\theta` 施加一个光滑性惩罚即可消除它，留作练习。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:222
#: 93dd6864300f44af811f8508e93726ed
msgid ""
"The whole gradient computation goes through the ``WeightedLaplace`` "
"assembler and the linear solve via the adjoint backward -- you never write a"
" sensitivity equation by hand."
msgstr "整个梯度计算经由 ``WeightedLaplace`` 装配器，并通过伴随反向传播穿过线性求解——你从不需要手写一条灵敏度方程。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:228
#: 0fd4a5e1b93a41fdb6a8d0bfed1ac70f
msgid "Worked example 2: thermal-compliance topology optimization"
msgstr "实战示例 2：热柔度拓扑优化"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:230
#: 5ba5c70ddc1149d4a85d0aa120edec34
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"For density-based topology optimization (compliance minimisation under a "
"volume constraint), TensorMesh ships a dedicated "
":class:`~tensormesh.optimizer.OCOptimizer` that implements the classical "
"Optimality Criteria update. Here we apply it to a thermal problem on "
":math:`[0,1]^2`: a Gaussian heat source in the centre, cold sinks at the "
"boundary, density :math:`\\rho \\in [0,1]` per element, SIMP conductivity "
":math:`\\kappa(\\rho) = \\kappa_{\\min} + (1 - "
"\\kappa_{\\min})\\,\\rho^{p}`, and a hard volume cap :math:`\\bar{\\rho} "
"\\leq V = 0.4`."
msgstr ""
"对于基于密度的拓扑优化（体积约束下的柔度最小化），TensorMesh 自带一个专用的 "
":class:`~tensormesh.optimizer.OCOptimizer`\\ ，实现了经典的最优性准则更新。这里我们将其应用于 "
":math:`[0,1]^2` 上的一个热问题：中心有一个高斯热源，边界处为冷汇，每个单元的密度 :math:`\\rho \\in [0,1]`\\ "
"，SIMP 导热率 :math:`\\kappa(\\rho) = \\kappa_{\\min} + (1 - "
"\\kappa_{\\min})\\,\\rho^{p}`\\ ，以及一个硬性体积上限 :math:`\\bar{\\rho} \\leq V = "
"0.4`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:283
#: 46fa5829d30e4eb89073e6930ead4eab
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Compliance drops from :math:`5.9 \\times 10^{-3}` (uniform grey plate) to "
":math:`6.9 \\times 10^{-4}` -- nearly an order of magnitude -- while the "
"volume constraint :math:`\\bar{\\rho} = 0.4` is held exactly throughout. The"
" optimal layout is a \"thermal cross\" connecting the hot source in the "
"centre to the cold sinks at the four mid-edges:"
msgstr ""
"柔度从 :math:`5.9 \\times 10^{-3}`\\ （均匀灰板）降至 :math:`6.9 \\times "
"10^{-4}`——几乎一个数量级——同时体积约束 :math:`\\bar{\\rho} = 0.4` "
"全程被精确保持。最优布局是一个“热十字”，把中心的热源与四条边中点处的冷汇连接起来："

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:294
#: 3c1c25e7814f477e84becc65610b1395
msgid ""
"Density evolution over 60 OC steps. Iteration 0 is the uniform :math:`\\rho "
"= V = 0.4` start; by iteration 5 the cross shape has emerged; iteration 59 "
"is the converged design. Compliance drops by :math:`\\sim 8.6\\times`; the "
"volume fraction is held at :math:`0.4` exactly."
msgstr ""
"60 步最优性准则迭代中的密度演化。第 0 次迭代是均匀的 :math:`\\rho = V = 0.4` 起点；到第 5 次迭代十字形状已经显现；第 "
"59 次迭代是收敛后的设计。柔度下降了约 :math:`\\sim 8.6\\times`\\ ；体积分数被精确保持在 :math:`0.4`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:300
#: db5309f70b5849818c9eba0e8c9a1b34
msgid ""
"The OC step uses the gradient just computed by autograd --- "
":meth:`tensormesh.optimizer.OCOptimizer.step` reads ``rho.grad``, finds the "
"Lagrange multiplier by bisection, and applies the density update with a move"
" limit. No finite differences, no hand-coded adjoint."
msgstr ""
"最优性准则步使用刚刚由 autograd 计算出的梯度——:meth:`tensormesh.optimizer.OCOptimizer.step` "
"读取 ``rho.grad``\\ ，通过二分法求出拉格朗日乘子，并在移动限制下施加密度更新。没有有限差分，也没有手写的伴随。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:308
#: 718ea11aeb9e48a9b891f727e9fccb6a
msgid "Wiring a neural network in"
msgstr "接入神经网络"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:310
#: 3962af436c1843838f6053595e75454f
msgid "Three patterns cover the common ML/PDE couplings:"
msgstr "三种模式涵盖了常见的机器学习/偏微分方程耦合："

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:312
#: 1e85e9ab51bb4d54a1bd329a85892a94
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**NN predicts a coefficient field.** The NN ingests coordinates (or features"
" derived from them) and outputs a per-node value --- feed the output to an "
"assembler via ``point_data={\"kappa\": nn_out}``. Gradients flow from the "
"FEM loss back through the NN."
msgstr ""
"**神经网络预测系数场。** 神经网络吃进坐标（或由其派生的特征），输出一个逐节点的值——通过 ``point_data={\"kappa\": "
"nn_out}`` 把输出喂给装配器。梯度会从有限元损失反向流过神经网络。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:317
#: a73229afa7be4bcc8b00221b1949a562
msgid ""
"**NN predicts boundary values.** Pass the output as ``dirichlet_value`` to a"
" freshly-built :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser`. The condensation contribution"
" to the RHS keeps the gradients connected."
msgstr ""
"**神经网络预测边界取值。** 把输出作为 ``dirichlet_value`` 传给一个新建的 "
":class:`~tensormesh.Condenser`\\ 。凝聚对右端项的贡献使梯度保持连通。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:321
#: 5369d66768da4c9890d0dbddb800987d
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**NN predicts per-element stiffness modifiers.** Stack the output into a "
"per-element tensor and pass it via ``element_data={\"alpha\": nn_out}``; let"
" the assembler's ``forward`` use it inside the integrand."
msgstr ""
"**神经网络预测逐单元的刚度调节因子。** 把输出堆叠成一个逐单元的张量，通过 ``element_data={\"alpha\": nn_out}``"
" 传入；让装配器的 ``forward`` 在被积函数内部使用它。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:326
#: 039bb6eb7a694cedbeb3dd2353ade646
msgid ""
"In all three the NN is a regular ``nn.Module`` and the FEM pipeline is a "
"regular sequence of ``nn.Module`` calls; standard ``torch.optim`` optimisers"
" work without any special hooks."
msgstr ""
"在这三种模式中，神经网络都是一个普通的 ``nn.Module``\\ ，有限元流水线则是一串普通的 ``nn.Module`` 调用；标准的 "
"``torch.optim`` 优化器无需任何特殊 hook 即可工作。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/differentiability.rst:332
#: bbcb3e88a9c34c1bb6d08dc774c075fa
msgid ""
"Wiring a network in needs **no** TensorMesh-specific neural-network layer --"
" a plain :class:`torch.nn.Module` is enough, as above. Today "
":mod:`tensormesh.nn` ships only the container utilities ``BufferDict`` and "
"``BufferList`` (used internally to register tensors as module buffers), not "
"learnable layers. Higher-level neural-operator and learnable-PDE building "
"blocks are planned for a future release; until then, build the network side "
"with ordinary ``torch.nn`` layers."
msgstr ""
"接入网络\\ **无需**\\ 任何 TensorMesh 专属的神经网络层——如上所示，一个普通的 :class:`torch.nn.Module` "
"就够了。目前 :mod:`tensormesh.nn` 只提供容器工具 ``BufferDict`` 和 ``BufferList``\\ "
"（在内部用于把张量注册为模块 buffer），并不包含可学习的层。更高层的神经算子与可学习偏微分方程构件已列入未来版本的计划；在那之前，请用普通的 "
"``torch.nn`` 层来搭建网络侧。"

